clings - A powerful CLI for Things 3 on macOS
Copyright (C) 2024 Dan Hart

This fork includes modifications by Drew Burchfield (2026):
- Added --when flag for scheduling todos via Things URL scheme
- Added --heading flag for organizing todos within project headings
- Added auth token management (clings config set-auth-token)
- Added AuthTokenStore with secure POSIX file operations
- Fixed README to match actual CLI commands

